Package eecalcs.conductors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Circuit
    This class represents a set of conductors inside a conduit.
    Coating
    Contains only static booleans constants indicating coating
    CondProp
    This class encapsulates static data and methods about properties of conductors as defined in NEC 2014 tables 310.15(B)(16), 8, 9, 5 and 5A.
    Conductor
    Encapsulates the properties and methods for a single conductor as a physical real life object.
    Insul
    Contains only static strings with the insulation valid types
    PropertySet
    This class encapsulates a set of all the electrical properties of a conductor as defined in NEC 2014 tables 310.15(B)(16), 8 and 9
    Size
    Contains only static strings with the conductor valid sizes
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Metal
    Defines the metal conductor types
